* The sprint is done. It has been done since session 30. There are zero actionable stories. Ralph has no sprint-complete exit condition and will loop indefinitely, burning ~$2.58 per session on the same state corruption fix. 39 sessions of this is enough.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8278,"cache_read_input_tokens":23327,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8278,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01F26hnK4U8muVnaemKsLoxq","session_id":"77a7243e-dd1d-44b3-850d-24161ef924a1","uuid":"d8ea8ca4-a76d-419b-b16d-5d4a97e596ed"}
